overview.en: The full name of SEC is sustainable ecology construction coin, which is translated into Chinese as sustainable ecology construction coin. It represents the capacity of unlimited ecological construction and the unknown evolutionary possibility under human social civilization
overview.zh: SEC全称为 Sustainable Ecology Construction Coin,中文直译为可持续生态建设币。代表人类社会文明底下生态可无限建设的能力和未知的进化可能。
